{"tid":547312,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"(港女老婆偷食有感) 有無人覺得連登仔真係好撚得閒？","createTime":"2018-02-01T10:19:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-01T10:38:34.000Z","uid":83128,"like":13,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"13e7c73127a4f8408a41de554b6cd24fe718919c","tid":547312,"uid":83128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T10:19:31.000Z","msg":"上熱門台見到開左N 個post 都係講呢單野<br />\n<br />\n我無追po詳情唔知 應該係有個人妻偷食 然後比人起底<br />\n<br />\n講真人地偷食關你地撚事咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你識事主？你同事主有親？人地家事 其實關你地班連登仔咩事 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n連登仔咁撚得閒 唔怪得咁廢又咁窮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c391c1e59b988715dd5b43220a205e2771e72ae4","tid":547312,"uid":83128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T10:20:22.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba7a0ab950910170e481585aef25e476c95037f5","tid":547312,"uid":83128,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T10:22:45.000Z","msg":"無人有同感？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6be411fa5370c2a06b5e66b0719cdbd423e8316f","tid":547312,"uid":76419,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T10:23:39.000Z","msg":"咁你又上連登？"},{"pid":"9bacc58f3595bb9373c74d53eb1e3298d18838a0","tid":547312,"uid":31962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T10:26:47.000Z","msg":"好心得閒睇下整合，咁簡單邊個會咁無聊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0dde7464e53a1aad7499d8a5b666ffcb9b7ed2cf","tid":547312,"uid":56157,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T10:27:39.000Z","msg":"因為本身條友拿自己同老婆畫漫畫放比公眾睇，仲透過咁去Sell各種產品(eg.利是封)。<br />\n咁突然本漫畫就完左，因為條友話同個老婆散